{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came in uniform occasionally, especially when there was holidays or when there were special celebrations to take place, which took place constantly and we were marched around.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the student-- the attitude of the students changed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were taunted very often, especially on days when they came in uniform, and beaten up very often on the way home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I got along fabulously with-- with the-- with the kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had no problems at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when those days came, you were beaten up, the next day they were as nice-- as nice as could be to us again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we really couldn't understand that it was like a mass hysteria, like a lynch mentality that took place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And well, it became a way of life after a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Jewish students, we sort of stuck together a little bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were not many of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And things became rather difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "During sporting-- sport events, no one dared to pick us for a team.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Herr Knodt, he was our gym teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was very sensitive, actually, to me personally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I cannot complain about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When they refused to pick me, if it's an odd number, he said, well, you join this team here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They need one more person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And if it's an even one, he said, I'm going to join you and Werner can join the other team.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he was really very considerate, considering that he was a very-- a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, something else came up that was-- that I found out later to be a ruling, that all the Jewish students would have to sit in the last row of the class and would no longer be called upon to-- you know, be called upon.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
